Postcode,Anywhere,is,an,information,as,a,service,provider,offering,over,separate,web,services,covering,a,broad,range,of,business,efficiency,tools,for,address,and,data,capture,validation,and,cleansing,to,geo,coding,mapping,and,route,planning,and,optimization,The,Customer,Profiling,API,assigns,classifications,to,contacts,based,on,their,postcode,It,uses,over,demographic,statistics,and,lifestyle,variables,from,the,ACORN,database,The,API,uses,a,number,of,protocols,including,REST,SOAP,and,XML,RPC,Responses,can,be,formatted,in,XML,JSON,CSV,HTML,and,PDF